nhc_headline: ...TROPICAL STORM CONDITIONS EXPECTED ON BAJA CALIFORNIA SUR LATER TODAY...
summary: ...TROPICAL STORM CONDITIONS EXPECTED ON BAJA CALIFORNIA SUR LATER TODAY... As of 5:00 AM MST Sat Oct 11 the center of Raymond was located near 21.4, -109.4 with movement NW at 16 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1002 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 45 mph.
